Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Adjust cursor position
Git-commit: 56fb276d0244d430496f249335a44ae114dd5f54
Patch-mainline: v6.11-rc4
Alt-commit: 8f9b23abbae5ffcd64856facd26a86b67195bc2f
